Hi,

Every game I currently am trying to play will not load in past the picks and bans. The template where the champions load pops up and then it says that it is not responding, so will not load. Then when I try to reconnect, it says I am not connected to the internet! This does not make sense, as I am still able to use the internet at the same time as it saying I apparently have no internet connection. This has led to me gaining a 5x20 minute queue increase. Not that this makes any difference, as I can't connect to any games anyway!

Any help on this situation at all would be greatly appreciated, because I can no longer play my favourite game!{{item:3070}}
